 has vacated his three heavyweight titles to focus on his recovery from “a serious medical condition’’ his management said in a statement late on Wednesday. October 13, 2016 In "News" Controversial boxer Tyson Fury moved closer to his dream all-British world heavyweight showdown with Anthony Joshua when he was told on Friday that he will get his licence back if he passes a medical. January 19, 2018 In "Sports"